import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { Person, PersonService } from '../person.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-list-persons', templateUrl: './list-persons.component.html', styleUrls: ['./list-persons.component.css'] }) export class ListPersonsComponent implements OnInit { persons?: Person[]; constructor(private personService: PersonService) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.personService.getAll().subscribe(persons => { this.persons = persons; }); } }
